        "html": "<div class=\"B1_text_xin\" id=\"cont\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><h2>观音心咒</h2>\n<p><span>ong<br>\n唵</span><span>ma<br>\n嘛</span><span>ni<br>\n呢</span><span>bei<br>\n叭</span><span>mei<br>\n咪</span><span>hong<br>\n吽</span></p>\n\n<h2>文殊菩萨心咒</h2>\n<p><span>ōng<br>\n嗡</span><span>ā<br>\n啊</span><span> rā<br>\n[日/阿]</span><span>，<br>\n，</span><span>bā<br>\n巴</span><span>zhā<br>\n扎</span><span>nà<br>\n那</span><span>dǐ<br>\n底</span><span>。<br>\n。</span></p>\n\n<h2>金刚萨埵心咒</h2>\n<p><span>ōng<br>\n嗡</span><span>bān<br>\n班</span><span>zhā<br>\n扎</span><span>er<br>\n尔</span><span>sà<br>\n萨</span><span>duǒ<br>\n埵</span><span>hōng<br>\n吽</span></p>\n\n<h2>阿弥陀佛心咒</h2>\n<p><span>Om<br>\n嗡</span><span>Amitabha<br>\n阿弥德瓦</span><span>Arya<br>\n阿耶</span><span>Siddhi<br>\n悉地</span><span>Hum<br>\n吽</span><span>Hrih<br>\n舍</span></p>\n\n<h2>虚空藏菩萨咒</h2>\n<p><span>ā<br>\n阿</span><span>nǐ<br>\n袮</span><span>，<br>\n，</span><span>luó<br>\n逻</span><span>shé<br>\n阇</span><span>pí<br>\n鞞</span><span>。<br>\n。</span><span>qián<br>\n钤</span><span>fú<br>\n浮</span><span>suō<br>\n娑</span><span>shé<br>\n阇</span><span>pí<br>\n鞞</span><span>。<br>\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>yē<br>\n耶</span><span>pó<br>\n婆</span><span>nài<br>\n奈</span><span>shé<br>\n阇</span><span>pí<br>\n鞞</span><span>。<br>\n。</span><span>bó<br>\n博</span><span>cè<br>\n厕</span><span>，<br>\n，</span><span>suō<br>\n娑</span><span>mí<br>\n迷</span><span>。<br>\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>bō<br>\n波</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span><span>luó<br>\n逻</span><span>shé<br>\n阇</span><span>pí<br>\n鞞</span><span>。<br>\n。</span><span>tuō<br>\n他</span><span>nài<br>\n奈</span><span>pó<br>\n婆</span><span>luó<br>\n逻</span><span>pí<br>\n鞞</span><span>。<br>\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>sà<br>\n萨</span><span>duō<br>\n多</span><span>luó<br>\n逻</span><span>qié<br>\n伽</span><span>luó<br>\n逻</span><span>ní<br>\n泥</span><span>。<br>\n。</span><span>xiū<br>\n休</span><span>mó<br>\n磨</span><span>xiū<br>\n休</span><span>mó<br>\n磨</span><span>。<br>\n。</span></p>\n<p><span