pan>hā<br>\n哈</span></p>\n\n\n<h2>解结咒</h2>\n<p>ōng。chǐ lìng jīn zā jīn zā shèng jīn zā。</p>\n<p>唵。齿令金匝金匝胜金匝。</p>\n<p>wǒ jīn wèi rǔ jiě jīn zā。</p>\n<p>我今为汝解金匝。</p>\n<p>zhōng bù wèi rǔ jié jīn zā。</p>\n<p>终不为汝结金匝。</p>\n<p>ōng。xiáng zhōng xiáng jí zhōng jí。</p>\n<p>唵。祥中祥。吉中吉。</p>\n<p>bō luó huì shàng yǒu zhū lí。</p>\n<p>波罗会上有珠琍。</p>\n<p>yī qiè yuān jiā huà jí xiáng。</p>\n<p>一切冤家化吉祥。</p>\n<p>mó hē bō ruò bō luó mì。</p>\n<p>摩诃般若波罗密。</p>\n\n<h2>月光菩萨咒</h2>\n<p><span>shēn<br>\n深</span><span>dī<br>\n低</span><span>dì<br>\n帝</span><span>tú<br>\n屠</span><span>sū<br>\n苏</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span></p>\n<p><span>ā<br>\n阿</span><span>ruò<br>\n若</span><span>mì<br>\n蜜</span><span>dì<br>\n帝</span><span>wū<br>\n乌</span><span>dū<br>\n都</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span></p>\n<p><span>shēn<br>\n深</span><span>qí<br>\n耆</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span></p>\n<p><span>bō<br>\n波</span><span>lài<br>\n赖</span><span>dì<br>\n帝</span></p>\n<p><span>yē<br>\n耶</span><span>mí<br>\n弥</span><span>ruò<br>\n若</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span><span>wū<br>\n乌</span><span>dū<br>\n都</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span></p>\n<p><span>jū<br>\n拘</span><span>luó<br>\n罗</span><span>dì<br>\n帝</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span><span>qí<br>\n耆</span><span>mó<br>\n摩</span><span>zhà<br>\n吒</span></p>\n<p><span>suō<br>\n沙</span><span>pó<br>\n婆</span><span>hē<br>\n诃</span></p>\n\n<h2>日光菩萨咒</h2>\n<p><span>ná<br>\n南</span><span>mó<br>\n无</span><span>bó<br>\n勃</span><span>tuó<br>\n陀</span><span>qú<br>\n瞿</span><span>nà<br>\n那</span><span>mí<br>\n迷</span></p>\n<p><span>ná<br>\n南</span><span>mó<br>\n无</span><span>dá<br>\n达</span><span>mó<br>\n摩</span><span>mò<br>\n莫</span><span>hē<br>\n诃</span><span>dī<br>\n低</span></p>\n<p><span>ná<br>\n南</span><span>mó<br>\n无</span><span>sēng<br>\n僧</span><span>qié<br>\n伽</span><span>duō<br>\n多</span><span>yè<br>\n夜</span><span>ní<br>\n泥</span></p>\n<p><span>dǐ<br>\n底</span><span>li<br>\n哩</span><span>bù<br>\n部</span><span>bì<br>\n毕</span><span>sà<br>\n萨</span><span>duō<br>\n咄</span><span>dá<br>\n檐</span><spa